Content: Pastor Alcorn was saved as a young boy at the age of 6. At the age of 19 the Lord began to stir his heart to be  a preacher of the Gospel. The Lord led him to The  Crown College in 2003 where he met his wife Julie. He  graduated with a Bachelors Degree in Pastoral Ministry  in 2006 and a Master of Ministry degree in 2007.  Brother Alcorn has been our pastor since November the 9th, 2008.
John Doe graduated from youth pastor university with a degree in youth pastoring.  He and his wife Jane teach our youth Bible study and help pastor run the youth ministries of our church.
When Jane started serving as our church secretary - they were still making new episodes of the Brady Bunch.  She's been faithfully serving for over 30 years.
